{2010501005|XXGpvertex|97|0|193|0|{|{30100001|XXparameter_set|@@@@{{30001002|XXparameter|!prototype_path|$AB_COMPONENTS/Transform/Reformat.mpc|3|2|Pf$|@{0|}}
{30001002|XXparameter|transform0|/*Reformat operation*/
out::reformat(in)=
begin


out.* :: in.* ;
out.deposit_date :: (date("YYYYMMDD"))(date("DDMMYYYY"))in.deposit_date;

out.fund_code :: string_lrtrim(in.fund_code) ;
//out.investment_structure :: string_lrtrim(in.investment_structure) ;
out.account_number :: if(starts_with(string_lrtrim(in.account_number),"0")) string_substring(string_lrtrim(in.account_number),2,string_length(string_lrtrim(in.account_number)))
                        else string_lrtrim(in.account_number);
out.ext_load_type :: string_filter_out(in.ext_load_type,"\\n");
out.filler :: "\\n";

end;|3|3|c|@{0|}}

decimal("\\x01",sign_reserved) market_value;
string("\\x01") fund_code ;
string("\\x01") load_type ;
string("\\x01") ext_load_type ;
string('\\n') filler ;

end|3|1|l|@{0|}}

{30001002|XXparameter|transform1|/*Reformat operation*/
out::reformat(in)=
begin

out.* :: in.* ;
out.birth_date_2 :: if(string_lrtrim(in.birth_date_2) =="0") " " else in.birth_date_2;

// out.brand_type :: if ( string_lrtrim(in.contract_type) member [ vector "REG-LIF","REG-RRIF","REG-LRIF", "REG-PRIF" ,"REG-RLIF" ] ) 'VI'
//                  else 'VS' ;

end;|3|1|l|@{0|}}
{30001002|XXparameter|output_index|/*Function returning index of output port*/
out::output_index(in)=
begin
out :: if(in.source_indicator == "S") 1 
       else if (in.source_indicator member [ vector "I"] ) 2
       else if (in.source_indicator member [ vector "G1"] ) 3
       else if (in.source_indicator member [ vector "G2"] ) 4
       else if (in.source_indicator member [ vector "C"] ) 5
       
       else if (in.source_indicator member [ vector "F"] ) 6
       else if (in.source_indicator member [ vector "R"] ) 7
       
       
       else 0;
end;|3|1|l|@{0|}}

{2010501005|XXGpvertex|194|0|441|0|{|{30100001|XXparameter_set|@@@@{{30001002|XXparameter|!prototype_path|$AB_COMPONENTS/Transform/Reformat.mpc|3|2|Pf$|@{0|}}
{30001002|XXparameter|transform0|/*Reformat operation*/
out::reformat(in)=
begin

                             
 let string(3) company_code = in.company_code;   
 

let  string(" ") pac_deposit_amount_1 = if (string_lrtrim(in.detail_segment.pac_deposit_amount) == '.00' ) '0.00'
                                            else  string_lrtrim(in.detail_segment.pac_deposit_amount) ;
                                            
let  decimal(" ") pac_deposit_amount_2 =  string_lrtrim(pac_deposit_amount_1) ;




let  decimal(6.2) pac_allocation_percentage_1 =  if (in.sum_pac_deposit_amount == 0) 0
                                                    else (decimal(6.2)) (( pac_deposit_amount_2/in.sum_pac_deposit_amount) * 100)  ;


let string(5) pac_allocation_percentage =  if (  string_length(string_lrtrim(pac_allocation_percentage_1) ) == 6 ) string_substring(string_lrtrim(pac_allocation_percentage_1),1,3)
                                           else  string_pad(string_lrtrim(pac_allocation_percentage_1),5)  ;


let decimal(19.2) pac_deposit_amount =  pac_deposit_amount_2 * pac_allocation_percentage_1 ;
  
  let string(1) v_amount_sign = if (in.detail_segment.current_market_value >= 0 ) '+' else '-' ;
  let string(12) amount_temp1 = string_lpad( string_lrtrim((decimal(12.2)) math_abs(in.detail_segment.current_market_value) ), 12, "0" ) ;
  
  //---------------------------------- units-------------------------
  
  
  
let decimal(14) units_temp1 =  if(in.price_dist_rate_accrual != 0.0) decimal_round_down(in.detail_segment.current_market_value/in.price_dist_rate_accrual, 3) else 0.000 ;
let string(1) units_temp_sign = if ( units_temp1 >= 0 ) '+' else '-' ;
let string(14)  units_temp =  decimal_lpad( string_lrtrim((decimal(14.3)) math_abs(units_temp1) ), 14, "0" ) ; 
  

  

let string(1) annualized_scheduled_payments_temp_sign = if ( in.awdAmount >= 0 ) '+' else '-' ;
let string(13) awdAmount = (string(13))  (decimal(13.2)) math_abs(in.awdAmount) ;
let string(13) annualized_scheduled_payments_temp  =  string_concat( annualized_scheduled_payments_temp_sign , string_lpad(string_lrtrim(awdAmount), 12, "0" ) )  ;


let string(1) rrif_minimum_annual_payment_temp_sign =  if ( first_defined(lookup('RIF_LIF lkp',in.master_segment.account_number).current_minimum,0.0) >= 0 ) '+' else '-' ;
let string(13) rrif_minimum_annual_payment_temp_amount = (string(13))  (decimal(13.2)) math_abs(first_defined(lookup('RIF_LIF lkp',in.master_segment.account_number).current_minimum,0.00)) ;
let string(13) rrif_minimum_annual_payment_temp = string_concat( rrif_minimum_annual_payment_temp_sign, string_lpad(string_lrtrim(rrif_minimum_annual_payment_temp_amount), 12, "0" ) )  ;

                 else if(in.source_indicator =="S") 
                           if ( !is_blank( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.hld_holding_name) ) ) string_concat(company_code,in.master_segment.hld_holding_name)  
                           else string_concat(company_code,string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_number))
                 else  string_concat(company_code,string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_number)) ;

               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) member [ vector  "P" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_2 
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) member [ vector  "P" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_3 
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) member [ vector  "N" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_1
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) member [ vector "N" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_2 
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) member [ vector "N" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_3 
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) == "S" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_1
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) == "S" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_2
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) == "S" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_3
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) not member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) member [ vector "J","L"] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_1
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) not member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) member  [ vector "J","L"]  ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_2
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) not member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3)  member  [ vector "J","L"]  ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_3  ;

               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) member [ vector  "N" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_2
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) member [ vector  "N" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_3
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) == "S" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_1

                                          string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.gmwb_effective_date) != "0" and
                                          gmwb_effective_date > lookup("segcons_header_prev_lkp").from_date and
                                          gmwb_effective_date <= lookup("segcons_header_lkp").from_date 
                                        ) "+000000000.00"

out.fund_type :: if ( string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I"] )
                             if (  string_lrtrim(first_defined(lookup("fund_lkp", string_lrtrim(in.detail_segment.fund_code)).product_series , ""))  member [ vector  "MMP","MMP EGB" ] ) "MMP"
                             else "R"
                 else string_substring(first_defined(lookup("irfi_fund_lkp",in.detail_segment.fund_code).irfi_fund_category,""),3,2) ;

out.fund_management_fee_rate ::  in.detail_segment.fund_management_fee_rate ;
out.fund_management_fee_tier :: in.detail_segment.fund_management_fee_tier ;
out.advisor_fee_rate :: in.master_segment.advisor_fee_rate ;

out.lib_era :: if ( string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I","G","G1","G2","C","F","P" , "R"] ) ""
               else if(in.master_segment.gmwb_rider_ind != "N")
                       if(in.master_segment.lib_era =="LIBE1") "1"
                       else if (in.master_segment.lib_era =="LIBE2") "2" 
                       else ""
                     
                else ""    ;
                             
                 
out.income_program_indicator :: "" ;
out.annuity_holding_account_fund_bal_indicator :: " " ;
out.rebate_rate :: in.detail_segment.rebate_rate ;
out.rebate_tier :: in.detail_segment.rebate_tier ;
out.distribution_chanel :: if ( string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I","G","G1","G2","C","F","P" , "R"] ) ""
                           else v_distribution_channel; 
                           
out.product_name :: if(in.source_indicator == "S") "" 
                    else if ( string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I","G","G1","G2","C","F","P" , "R"] ) ""
                    else product_name ; 


out.pac_allocation_percentage ::pac_allocation_percentage ;

out.pac_base_amount :: pac_deposit_amount ;
out.high_net_worth_invested_indicator :: if(string_prefix(in.master_segment.investment_structure,1) member [vector "A","B"]) "Y"  else "N" ;


out.gmbr_maturity_benefit_guarantee_amount :: if ( string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I","G","G1","G2","C","F","P" , "R"] ) "" 
                                              else gmbr_maturity_benefit_guarantee_amount  ;

                
                                   
 
out.gmbr_maturity_guarantee_date ::  if ( string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I","G","G1","G2","C","F","P" , "R"] ) "" 
                                     else if ( string_lrtrim(contract_type) member [ vector "REG-LIF","REG-RRIF","REG-LRIF", "REG-PRIF" ,"REG-RLIF" ] ) 

                                             if ( in.detail_segment.policy_maturity_date == 0 ) '21411231'

                                             else string_pad(string_lrtrim(in.detail_segment.policy_maturity_date),8,"0")

                                     else

                                             if ( in.detail_segment.policy_maturity_date == 0 ) '0'

                                             else string_pad(string_lrtrim(in.detail_segment.policy_maturity_date),8,"0") ;
                                  
                                   
                                   
                                   
                                   

  out.record_count :: in.record_count;


 
 out.deposit_back_end_charge :: "" ;
 out.deferred_acquisition_amount :: "" ;
  out.fund_code :: in.detail_segment.fund_code;
  
  out.contract_number :: in.detail_segment.contract_number ;

{30001002|XXparameter|transform|/*Join transform*/

{30001002|XXparameter|transform0|/*Reformat operation*/
out::reformat(in)=
begin


let decimal('') accountAttribute_count = first_defined( length_of(in.accountAttribute) , 0 ) ;

let decimal('') acct_awd_count = first_defined( length_of(in.accountAWD), 0 ) ;

let decimal('') acctinvestment_awd_count = first_defined( length_of(in.accountInvestmentAWD) , 0 ) ;
let decimal(13.2) amount_temp = 0 ;
let decimal (",") acctinvestment_awd_active_reccod_count = 0 ;
let decimal (",") acctinvestment_awd_MIN_reccod_count = 0 ;
let decimal (",") acctinvestment_awd_GRS_reccod_count = 0 ;
let decimal (",") acctinvestment_awd_NET_reccod_count = 0 ;
 let string("\\x01") temp_split_option_code_RRIF_flag="N";
  let string("\\x01") temp_split_option_code_LIF_flag="N";
 ////let string("\\x01") temp_split_option_code_AWD="";

let string(2) awd_frequency = ' ' ;
let decimal('') awd_seq_no = 0 ;
let decimal("") awd_frequency_value = 0 ;                                   
let string("") temp_acct_attribute_code = ' ' ;
let string("")  temp_acct_attribute_MDB = ' ' ;

let int x =0;
let int y =0;

let string(",") seg_flag = "N" ;

/*

for (let int k, k < acct_awd_count )
begin
awd_frequency = if ( string_lrtrim(in.accountAWD[k].awdStatus) == 'AC' ) first_defined( in.accountAWD[k].awdFrequency, awd_frequency)
                else awd_frequency ;

awd_seq_no = if ( string_lrtrim(in.accountAWD[k].awdStatus) == 'AC' ) in.accountAWD[k].awdSeqNo
                else awd_seq_no ;

end
*/

for ( let int l, l < acctinvestment_awd_count )
begin
         begin block acctawd


            for (let int m, m < acct_awd_count )
              begin
                   if (  string_lrtrim(in.accountAWD[m].awdStatus) == "AC" and 
                         in.accountAWD[m].awdSeqNo == in.accountInvestmentAWD[l].awdSeqNo and
                         first_defined(lookup("investment_lkp",in.accountInvestmentAWD[l].investmentCode).productTypeCode, "") == "SEG" 
                      )
                      
                             begin

                                 awd_frequency = in.accountAWD[m].awdFrequency;
                                 awd_seq_no = in.accountAWD[m].awdSeqNo ;
                                 seg_flag = "Y" ;
                                 exit acctawd ;

                             end

               end 
        
         end block acctawd
end


awd_frequency_value =    if ( string_lrtrim(awd_frequency) == "MO" )  12
                         else if ( string_lrtrim(awd_frequency) == "SM" )  24
                         else if ( string_lrtrim(awd_frequency) == "BW" )  26
                         else if ( string_lrtrim(awd_frequency) == "BM" )  6
                         else if ( string_lrtrim(awd_frequency) == "QT" )  4
                         else if ( string_lrtrim(awd_frequency) == "SA" )  2
                         else if ( string_lrtrim(awd_frequency) == "AN" ) 1
                         else 0 ;


for (let int i, i< accountAttribute_count)
begin


temp_acct_attribute_code = if ( string_lrtrim(in.accountAttribute[i].acctAttributeCode) member [vector 'ZSFF1', 'ZSFF2','YSMW1', 'YSMW2', 'XSEP1', 'XSEP2', 'ZSFN1', 'ZSFN2'] ) string_lrtrim(in.accountAttribute[i].acctAttributeCode) 
                            else temp_acct_attribute_code ;


temp_acct_attribute_MDB = if ( string_lrtrim(in.accountAttribute[i].acctAttributeCode) member [vector 'ZSFF1', 'ZSFF2','YSMW1', 'YSMW2', 'XSEP1', 'XSEP2', 'ZSFN1', 'ZSFN2'] ) string_lrtrim(in.accountAttribute[i].acctAttributeCode) 
                            else temp_acct_attribute_code ;
end




for (let int j, j< acctinvestment_awd_count )
begin


 ///amount_temp =  if ( awd_seq_no == in.accountInvestmentAWD[j].awdSeqNo  ) (decimal(13.2))  ( amount_temp + ( first_defined(in.accountInvestmentAWD[j].amount,0) * awd_frequency_value) )  
                 ///else amount_temp ;

acctinvestment_awd_active_reccod_count =  if ( awd_seq_no == in.accountInvestmentAWD[j].awdSeqNo  ) (acctinvestment_awd_active_reccod_count + 1)
                                          else acctinvestment_awd_active_reccod_count ;

acctinvestment_awd_MIN_reccod_count =    if ( awd_seq_no == in.accountInvestmentAWD[j].awdSeqNo and string_lrtrim(in.accountInvestmentAWD[j].contrRedmCode) == 'IFPAY'  ) (acctinvestment_awd_MIN_reccod_count + 1)
                                         else acctinvestment_awd_MIN_reccod_count ;
                                         
acctinvestment_awd_GRS_reccod_count =    if ( awd_seq_no == in.accountInvestmentAWD[j].awdSeqNo and string_lrtrim(in.accountInvestmentAWD[j].grossNetInd) == 'G'   ) (acctinvestment_awd_GRS_reccod_count + 1)
                                         else acctinvestment_awd_GRS_reccod_count ;
                                         
acctinvestment_awd_NET_reccod_count =    if ( awd_seq_no == in.accountInvestmentAWD[j].awdSeqNo and string_lrtrim(in.accountInvestmentAWD[j].grossNetInd) == 'N'  ) (acctinvestment_awd_NET_reccod_count + 1)
                                         else acctinvestment_awd_NET_reccod_count ;                                         

end

//////////////////////////////////////
 
for ( y,y< first_defined(length_of(in.accountRRIF),0))
begin

        if(in.accountRRIF[y].splitOptionCode member [ vector "W","%"])
                         temp_split_option_code_RRIF_flag="Y";

end 

for ( y,y< first_defined(length_of(in.accountLIF),0))
begin

        if(in.accountLIF[y].splitOptionCode member [ vector "W","%"])
                         temp_split_option_code_LIF_flag="Y";

end 





/////////////////////////////////////////////////////
if(is_defined(in.accountRRIF) && string_upcase(string_lrtrim(in.account.acctType)) member [ vector "RRIF", "PRIF" ] && temp_split_option_code_RRIF_flag=="Y")
begin

        for ( x,x< first_defined(length_of(in.accountRRIF),0))
        begin
                if(in.accountRRIF[x].splitOptionCode member [ vector "W","%"])
                         amount_temp= amount_temp + first_defined(in.accountRRIF[x].reqAnnualPayment,0);
        end        
end

else if(is_defined(in.accountLIF) && string_upcase(string_lrtrim(in.account.acctType)) member [ vector "LIF", "LRIF" ] && temp_split_option_code_LIF_flag=="Y")
begin

        for ( x,x< first_defined(length_of(in.accountLIF),0))
        begin
                if(in.accountLIF[x].splitOptionCode member [vector  "W","%"])
                         amount_temp= amount_temp + first_defined(in.accountLIF[x].reqAnnualPayment,0);
        end        
end
else if(is_defined(in.accountSeg_FV) && string_upcase(string_lrtrim(in.account.acctType))=="CASH" &&   first_defined(lookup("INT:SEGCONS_PROCESSED","MST",in.account.accountNo).master_segment.lib_era,"") member [vector "LIBE1","LIBE2"])      // first_defined(in.accountSeg.awdSpltOpt,"")=="%")
begin       
                amount_temp= amount_temp + first_defined(in.accountSeg_FV.awdAmt,0);
        
end
else 
begin

        for (x,x< acctinvestment_awd_count)
        begin
        
               begin block accawd

                for (let int z, z < acct_awd_count )

                begin
                   if (( string_lrtrim(in.accountAWD[z].awdStatus) == 'AC' ) and in.accountAWD[z].awdSeqNo == in.accountInvestmentAWD[x].awdSeqNo and first_defined(lookup("investment_lkp",in.accountInvestmentAWD[x].investmentCode).productTypeCode, "") == "SEG"   )

                        begin

                                 awd_frequency = in.accountAWD[z].awdFrequency;

                                 exit accawd;

                        end

                

                end

                end block accawd
                

                awd_frequency_value =    if ( string_lrtrim(awd_frequency) == "MO" )  12

                                         else if ( string_lrtrim(awd_frequency) == "SM" )  24

                                         else if ( string_lrtrim(awd_frequency) == "BW" )  26

                                         else if ( string_lrtrim(awd_frequency) == "BM" )  6

                                         else if ( string_lrtrim(awd_frequency) == "QT" )  4

                                         else if ( string_lrtrim(awd_frequency) == "SA" )  2

                                         else if ( string_lrtrim(awd_frequency) == "AN" ) 1

                                         else 0 ;

                                        

                amount_temp =  (decimal(13.2))  ( amount_temp + ( first_defined(in.accountInvestmentAWD[x].amount,0) * awd_frequency_value) ) ;

       

                

        end

 

 

end

                
                








  out.accountNo :: in.account.accountNo ;
  out.awdAmount :: if ( seg_flag == "Y" ) amount_temp 
                   else 0 ;
  out.awdFrequency :: awd_frequency ;
  out.companyCode :: in.account.companyCode;
  out.accountAWD :: in.accountAWD;
  out.accountInvestmentAWD :: in.accountInvestmentAWD;
  out.acctattributecode :: temp_acct_attribute_code ;
  out.account :: in.account;
  
  out.payment_option :: if (acctinvestment_awd_active_reccod_count == 0) ' '
                        else if ( acctinvestment_awd_active_reccod_count == acctinvestment_awd_MIN_reccod_count) 'MIN'
                        else if ( acctinvestment_awd_active_reccod_count == acctinvestment_awd_GRS_reccod_count) 'GRS'
                        else if ( acctinvestment_awd_active_reccod_count == acctinvestment_awd_NET_reccod_count) 'NET'
                        else ' ' ;
  out.rrif_flag :: temp_split_option_code_RRIF_flag;
  out.lif_flag :: temp_split_option_code_LIF_flag;
  out.accountSeg_FV :: in.accountSeg_FV;
  
end;|3|3|c|@{0|}}

{30001002|XXparameter|transform|include "~$AI_XFR/uni_util_transform.xfr";

out :: join(in0, in1) =
begin


//let string("\\x01")[int] fund_lookup_vec = allocate_with_defaults();
  
    
 let string("\|") vs_source_indicator = derive_companyCode_from_accountNo(string_lrtrim(in0.master_segment.account_number)).vs_source_indicator ;
 //let string('\|') vs_company_code=derive_companyCode_from_accountNo(string_lrtrim(in0.master_segment.account_number)).vs_company_code ;
 let string("\\x01") vs_fund_lookup_vec = in0.detail_segment[0].fund_code ; // derive_companyCode_from_accountNo(string_lrtrim(in0.master_segment.account_number)).vs_fund_lookup_vec ;
 
 let string('\|') vs_company_code= string_lrtrim(lookup("irfi_fund_lkp",vs_fund_lookup_vec).company_code) ;
 
vs_source_indicator =      if ( string_lrtrim(lookup("irfi_fund_lkp",vs_fund_lookup_vec).Legacy_System) == "IB15" ) "I"
                           else if ( string_lrtrim(lookup("irfi_fund_lkp",vs_fund_lookup_vec).product_series_code) == "GEN" ) "G"   
                           else if ( string_lrtrim(lookup("irfi_fund_lkp",vs_fund_lookup_vec).product_series_code) == "GN1" ) "G1"   
                           else if ( string_lrtrim(lookup("irfi_fund_lkp",vs_fund_lookup_vec).product_series_code) == "GN2" ) "G2"   
                           else if ( string_lrtrim(lookup("irfi_fund_lkp",vs_fund_lookup_vec).product_series_code) == "GNC" ) "C"   
                           else if ( string_lrtrim(lookup("irfi_fund_lkp",vs_fund_lookup_vec).product_series_code) == "FLX" ) "F"   
                           else if ( string_lrtrim(lookup("irfi_fund_lkp",vs_fund_lookup_vec).Legacy_System) == "PIP" ) "P" 
                           else vs_source_indicator ;



  out.irfi_fund_category :: first_defined(lookup("irfi_fund_lkp",vs_fund_lookup_vec).irfi_fund_category,"");
  out.fund_lookup_vec :: vs_fund_lookup_vec ;
  out.record_type :: in0.record_type;
  out.record_count :: in0.record_count;
  out.master_segment :: in0.master_segment;
  out.detail_count :: in0.detail_count;
  out.detail_segment :: in0.detail_segment;
  out.summary_segment :: in0.summary_segment;
  
  //out.acctattributecode :: first_defined(in1.ACCTATTR[0].acctAttributeCode, ' ') ;
  out.acctattributecode :: first_defined(in1.acctattributecode, ' ' ) ;
  
  
  //out.awdAmount :: first_defined(in2.amount,0) ;
  out.awdAmount :: first_defined(in1.awdAmount,0) ;
  
  //out.awdFrequency :: first_defined(in2.accountAWD[0].awdFrequency, ' ') ;
  out.awdFrequency :: first_defined(in1.awdFrequency, ' ') ;


out.policy_maturity_date :: if ( is_null(in1.account.specialHandling.acctMaturityDate) or in1.account.specialHandling.acctMaturityDate == 0 ) ' '
                            else string_pad(string_lrtrim(in1.account.specialHandling.acctMaturityDate),8) ;
  out.payment_option :: first_defined(in1.payment_option, ' ') ;
  out.acctEffectiveDate :: in1.account.specialHandling.acctEffectiveDate;
  out.source_indicator :: vs_source_indicator;
  out.company_code :: first_defined(vs_company_code,"");
  out.guarWdAmt :: in1.accountSeg_FV.guarWdAmt ;
   
end;|3|3|c|@{0|}}

{2010501005|XXGpvertex|895|0|2529|0|{|{30100001|XXparameter_set|@@@@{{30001002|XXparameter|!prototype_path|$AB_COMPONENTS/Transform/Reformat.mpc|3|2|Pf$|@{0|}}
{30001002|XXparameter|transform0|/*Reformat operation*/
out::reformat(in)=
begin


if (in.error_count > 5) 
force_abort(string_concat('','comp valuation rejects_from_Join_acct_num1 component more than 5 rejected records encountered - STOP processing and assign Incident to UNITRAX Support for their followup. include file'));


out.error_count :: in.error_count;
end;|3|3|c|@{0|}}
{30001002|XXparameter|_propagate_through|metadata type: out = in
metadata type: in = out|3|1|l|@{0|}}
{30001002|XXparameter|in_metadata||3|8|s=|@{0|}}

{2010501005|XXGpvertex|1115|0|3138|0|{|{30100001|XXparameter_set|@@@@{{30001002|XXparameter|!prototype_path|$AB_COMPONENTS/Transform/Reformat.mpc|3|2|Pf$|@{0|}}
{30001002|XXparameter|transform0|/*Reformat operation*/
out::reformat(in)=
begin
                             
                                                         
 let string(3) company_code = in.company_code;                               
                             

let string(1) v_amount_sign = if (in.summary_segment.guaranteed_maturity_value >= 0 ) '+' else '-' ;
let string(12) amount_temp1 = string_lpad( string_lrtrim((decimal(12.2)) math_abs(in.summary_segment.guaranteed_maturity_value) ), 12, "0" ) ;

let string(1) annualized_scheduled_payments_temp_sign = if ( in.awdAmount >= 0 ) '+' else '-' ;
let string(13) awdAmount = (string(13))  (decimal(13.2)) math_abs(in.awdAmount) ;
let string(13) annualized_scheduled_payments_temp  =  string_concat( annualized_scheduled_payments_temp_sign , string_lpad(string_lrtrim(awdAmount), 12, "0" ) )  ;


let string(1) rrif_minimum_annual_payment_temp_sign =  if ( first_defined(lookup('RIF_LIF lkp',in.master_segment.account_number).current_minimum,0.0) >= 0 ) '+' else '-' ;
let string(13) rrif_minimum_annual_payment_temp_amount = (string(13))  (decimal(13.2)) math_abs(first_defined(lookup('RIF_LIF lkp',in.master_segment.account_number).current_minimum,0.00)) ;
let string(13) rrif_minimum_annual_payment_temp = string_concat( rrif_minimum_annual_payment_temp_sign, string_lpad(string_lrtrim(rrif_minimum_annual_payment_temp_amount), 12, "0" ) )  ;

 
let string(1) minimum_annual_payment_temp_sign = if ( in.master_segment.contract_rrif_min >= 0 ) '+' else '-' ;
let string(12) minimum_annual_payment_temp = string_lpad( string_lrtrim ( (decimal(12.2)) math_abs(in.master_segment.contract_rrif_min) ), 12, "0" ) ;


let string(",") product_name =  if ( string_lrtrim(in.acctattributecode) member [vector 'ZSFF1', 'ZSFF2','YSMW1', 'YSMW2', 'XSEP1', 'XSEP2', 'ZSFN1', 'ZSFN2'])
                                    if ( string_lrtrim(in.acctattributecode) member [vector 'ZSFF1', 'ZSFN1'] ) 'Freedom Funds - era 1'
                                    else if ( string_lrtrim(in.acctattributecode) member [vector 'ZSFF2', 'ZSFN2'] ) 'Freedom Funds - era 2'
                                    else if ( string_lrtrim(in.acctattributecode) member [vector 'YSMW1'] ) 'Marketwatch - era 1'
                                    else if ( string_lrtrim(in.acctattributecode) member [vector 'YSMW2'] ) 'Marketwatch - era 2'
                                    else if ( string_lrtrim(in.acctattributecode) member [vector 'XSEP1'] ) 'Estate Protection - era 1'
                                    else  'Estate Protection - era 2'                                   
                                   
                                else if ( string_like(in.detail_segment[0].fund_code,'Z%') ) 'Freedom Funds - era 3'
                                else if ( string_like(in.detail_segment[0].fund_code,'Y%') ) 'MarketWatch - era 3' 
                                else if ( string_like(in.detail_segment[0].fund_code,'X%') ) 'Estate Protection - era 3' 
                                else "";

 

let string(1) v_gmbr_maturity_benefit_guarantee_amount_sign = if ( in.summary_segment.guaranteed_maturity_value >= 0) '+' else '-' ;
let string(15) gmbr_maturity_benefit_guarantee_amount = string_concat( v_gmbr_maturity_benefit_guarantee_amount_sign , string_lpad( string_lrtrim( (decimal(14.2)) math_abs(in.summary_segment.guaranteed_maturity_value)),14, '0') )  ;  
                                                                               
let string("\\x01")  contract_type =     if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type) == "RRSP" ) "REG-RRSP"
                               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type) == "LIRA" ) "REG-LIRA"
                               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type) == "CASH" ) "N-REG"
                               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type) == "RRIF" ) "REG-RRIF"
                               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type) == "LIF" ) "REG-LIF"
                               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type) == "LRIF" ) "REG-LRIF"
                               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type) == "RLIF" ) "REG-RLIF"
                               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type) == "PRIF" ) "REG-PRIF" 
                               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type) == "LRSP" ) "REG-LRSP"
                               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type) == "RLSP" ) "REG-RLSP"
				else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type) == "TFSA" ) "TFSA"
                             
                                
                               else if ( is_blank(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type)) && string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) == "RRSP" ) "REG-RRSP"
                               else if ( is_blank(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type)) && string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) == "LIRA" ) "REG-LIRA"
                               else if ( is_blank(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type)) && string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) == "CASH" ) "N-REG"
                               else if ( is_blank(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type)) && string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) == "RRIF" ) "REG-RRIF"
                               else if ( is_blank(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type)) && string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) == "LIF" ) "REG-LIF"
                               else if ( is_blank(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type)) && string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) == "LRIF" ) "REG-LRIF"
                               else if ( is_blank(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type)) && string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) == "RLIF" ) "REG-RLIF"
                               else if ( is_blank(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type)) && string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) == "PRIF" ) "REG-PRIF" 
                               else if ( is_blank(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type)) && string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) == "LRSP" ) "REG-LRSP"
                               else if ( is_blank(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type)) && string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) == "RLSP" ) "REG-RLSP"
			       else if ( is_blank(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.nominee_account_type)) && string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) == "TFSA" ) "TFSA";
                                
                                
  let string("\\x01") dob1 = if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) member [ vector  "P" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_1
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) member [ vector  "P" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_2 
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) member [ vector  "P" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_3 
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) member [ vector  "N" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_1
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) member [ vector "N" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_2 
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) member [ vector "N" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_3 
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) == "S" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_1
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) == "S" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_2
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) == "S" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_3
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) not member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) member [ vector "J","L"] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_1
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) not member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) member  [ vector "J","L"]  ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_2
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) not member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3)  member  [ vector "J","L"]  ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_3  ;
             
   let string ("\\x01") gender1= if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) member [ vector  "P" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_1
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) member [ vector  "P" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_2
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) member [ vector  "P" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_3
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) member [ vector  "N" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_1
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) member [ vector  "N" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_2
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) member [ vector  "N" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_3
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) == "S" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_1
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) == "S" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_2
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) == "S" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_3
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) not member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) member  [ vector "J","L"] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_1
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) not member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) member  [ vector "J","L"]) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_2
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) not member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) member  [ vector "J","L"]) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_3  ;
 
 
 
 let string("") life_indicator_2  = "";
 let string("") birth_date2= "";
 let string("") gender2= "";
  let string("") actual_date_of_death_2 = "";
  let string("") date_of_death_notification_2 = "";
  
  let string("") ride_type_indicator = if(in.master_segment.gmwb_rider_ind =="Y") string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.rider_type_ind)
                                       else "" ;  
                           
  
  let string(3) v_distribution_channel="";
  
  
  let string("") brand_type = if(in.source_indicator == "S")
                                  if (string_prefix(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.investment_structure),1) == "C") "D"
                                  else if (string_substring(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.investment_structure),2,1) == "A") "C"
                                   else if (string_substring(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.investment_structure),2,1) == "B") "I"
                                   else if (string_substring(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.investment_structure),2,1) == "C") "E"
                                    else ""
                              else if (in.source_indicator == "I") 
                                    if ( lookup_match("dthprocessrul", string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.investment_structure)) )
                                          if (   is_blank( string_lrtrim(lookup("dthprocessrul", string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.investment_structure)).accountAttribute) ) and  
                                                 string_lrtrim(lookup("dthprocessrul", string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.investment_structure)).reductionRule_) member [ vector "2","3" ]
                                             ) "D"
                                          else if (   is_blank( string_lrtrim(lookup("dthprocessrul", string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.investment_structure)).accountAttribute) ) ) "P"
                                          else "D"
                                    else "D"
                              else "";
                            
  
  let string(2) v_brand_type = if(in.source_indicator == "V")
                                      if ( string_lrtrim(contract_type) member [ vector "REG-LIF","REG-RRIF","REG-LRIF", "REG-PRIF" ,"REG-RLIF" ] ) 'VI'
                                      else 'VS'                 
                               else brand_type;
                               
let string(",") master_segment_ytd_gmwb_withdrawal = if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.ytd_gmwb_withdrawal) == ".00" ) "0"
                                                     else string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.ytd_gmwb_withdrawal) ;
                                                     
                                                     

let string(",") curr_year = string_lrtrim(string_substring( lookup("segcons_header_prev_lkp").from_date,1,4)) ;
let string(",") gmwb_effective_date =  string_concat(curr_year,string_substring(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.gmwb_effective_date),5,4) ) ;                 
                                                     

let decimal(12.2) ytd_gmwb_withdrawl = if ( !is_null(in.master_segment.gmwb_effective_date) and !is_blank(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.gmwb_effective_date)) and
                                          string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.gmwb_effective_date) != "0" and
                                          gmwb_effective_date > lookup("segcons_header_prev_lkp").from_date and
                                          gmwb_effective_date <= lookup("segcons_header_lkp").from_date 
                                        ) 0.00
                                     else 
                                        (decimal(12.2)) ( (decimal("")) master_segment_ytd_gmwb_withdrawal + (decimal("")) ( first_defined(lookup("gmwb_ytd_withdrawal_diff",in.master_segment.account_number).withdrawal_diff,0) ) ) ;
                             
							 
                                                         
 
if(in.source_indicator == "S")
begin
   if((in.master_segment.gmwb_rider_ind == "Y" and ride_type_indicator == "3")   or  in.master_segment.gmwb_rider_ind == "N"   )
   begin
       if (in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1 member [vector "J", "L","N"])
       begin 
            birth_date2=in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_1;
            gender2=in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_1;
       end
       else if (in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2 member [vector "J", "L","N"] )
       begin 
            birth_date2=in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_2;
            gender2=in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_2;
       
       end
       else if (in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3 member [vector "J", "L","N"] and is_blank(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2 ))
       begin 
            birth_date2=in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_3;
            gender2=in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_3;           
       end
      else if (in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1 member [vector "S" ])
       begin 
            birth_date2=in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_1;
            gender2=in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_1;
       end
       
       
       else if (in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2 member [vector "S"] )
       begin 
            birth_date2=in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_2;
            gender2=in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_2;
       
       end
       else if (in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3 member [vector "S" ] and is_blank(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2 ))
       begin 
            birth_date2=in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_3;
            gender2=in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_3;
       end         
  end                               
 else if  (in.master_segment.gmwb_rider_ind == "Y" and ride_type_indicator == "4")
 begin 
       if (in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1 member [vector "J", "L","N"])
       begin 
            birth_date2=in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_1;
            gender2=in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_1;
       end
       else if (in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2 member [vector "J", "L","S","N"] )
       begin 
            birth_date2=in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_2;
            gender2=in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_2;
       
       end
       else if ( in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3 member [vector "J", "L","S","N"] ) // and is_blank(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2 ))
       begin 
            birth_date2=in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_3;
            gender2=in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_3;           
       end
          
  end                              
end            
 
 //////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
 
 
 
                                


if((in.master_segment.gmwb_rider_ind == "Y" and ride_type_indicator == "3") or in.master_segment.gmwb_rider_ind == "N")
begin
   if (in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1 member [vector "J", "S","N"]  or in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2 member [vector "J", "S","N"] or in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3 member [vector "J", "S","N"])
   begin 
       if(is_blank(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.actual_date_of_death_2)) or string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.actual_date_of_death_2) == "0")
         life_indicator_2  = "0";
       else
         life_indicator_2  = "1";
   end      

   else
       life_indicator_2  = "";

end

else if (in.master_segment.gmwb_rider_ind == "Y" and ride_type_indicator == "4")
begin

       if (in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1 member [vector "J", "S","L","N"]  or in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2 member [vector "J", "S","L","N" ] or in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3 member [vector "J", "S","L","N"])
   begin 
       if(is_blank(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.actual_date_of_death_2)) or string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.actual_date_of_death_2) == "0" )
         life_indicator_2  = "0";
       else
         life_indicator_2  = "1";
   end      

   else
       life_indicator_2  = "";


end

else 
      life_indicator_2  = "";
 
 /////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
 
 

if((in.master_segment.gmwb_rider_ind == "Y" and ride_type_indicator == "3") or in.master_segment.gmwb_rider_ind == "N")
begin
        if (in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1 member [vector "J", "S","N"]  or in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2 member [vector "J", "S","N"] or in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3 member [vector "J", "S","N"])
        begin 
             if (life_indicator_2 != "0")
             begin
             actual_date_of_death_2 = in.master_segment.actual_date_of_death_2;
             date_of_death_notification_2 = in.master_segment.date_of_notification_of_death_2;
             
             end
        end
end
else if (in.master_segment.gmwb_rider_ind == "Y" and ride_type_indicator == "4")
begin
      if (in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1 member [vector "L","N"]  or in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2 member [vector "L" ,"N"] or in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3 member [vector "L","N"])
      begin
           if (life_indicator_2 != "0")
             begin
             actual_date_of_death_2 = in.master_segment.actual_date_of_death_2;
             date_of_death_notification_2 = in.master_segment.date_of_notification_of_death_2;
             
             end
       end
 
end 
 
 
 
 
 if( in.company_code == "GWL")
        v_distribution_channel = "GWD";       
else if (in.company_code == "LON")
        v_distribution_channel = "LLD";
else if  (in.company_code == "CAN")    
      begin
           if(in.master_segment.dealer_code == "3439")
           begin
                if( first_defined(string_lrtrim(string_upcase(lookup("SIEBEL_Other_Id_File",in.master_segment.rep_code).OtherIDType)),"") == "LONDON LIFE")
                        v_distribution_channel = "LLD";

                else  
                        v_distribution_channel = "GWD";
           end
           else   
                        v_distribution_channel = "CLD"; 
 
       end
 
 
 
 
 //////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

out.record_sequence :: 1 ; 

out.record_type :: "D" ;
out.company :: if ( string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I"] ) "GWL"
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "G","G1","G2","C","F","P", "R"] ) "CAN"
               else company_code ;

out.brand_name ::  if ( string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I"] ) "GWLSEG"
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "G","G1","G2","C","F","P", "R"] ) "CANSEG"
               else string_concat(company_code,"SEG");
               

                  
                  
 out.brand_type :: if ( string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "G","G1","G2","C","F","P" , "R"] ) "" 
                   else v_brand_type ;

                  
                  
                  
out.account_number :: in.master_segment.account_number ;
out.header :: "AA" ;

out.dt ::  if ( string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I","G","G1","G2","C","F","P" , "R"] ) first_defined(lookup("Fund_entry_cross_ref",in.detail_segment[0].account_number).min_trade_date ,"")
           else if(in.source_indicator == "S")
                       if(brand_type member [vector "C", "I" ,"D"]) in.detail_segment[0].fund_entry_date
                       else if (brand_type == "E" and in.master_segment.gurantee_reset_option member [vector "1","2"]) in.detail_segment[0].fund_entry_date
                       else if ( in.master_segment.reset_stop_date == in.policy_maturity_date ) in.detail_segment[0].fund_entry_date                        
                       else if (in.master_segment.reset_stop_date == '0') in.detail_segment[0].fund_entry_date
                          
                       else  
                       in.master_segment.reset_stop_date
            else in.acctEffectiveDate ;
             

out.fund_code :: " " ;

                          else if ( (decimal(""))in.summary_segment.guaranteed_maturity_value <0.0 )  decimal_lpad(in.summary_segment.guaranteed_maturity_value,13)
              else if(in.source_indicator=="S" and (decimal(""))in.summary_segment.guaranteed_maturity_value >=0.0 ) string_concat("+",decimal_lpad(in.summary_segment.guaranteed_maturity_value,12)) 
              else if (in.source_indicator=="S" and (decimal(""))in.summary_segment.guaranteed_maturity_value <0.0 )  decimal_lpad(in.summary_segment.guaranteed_maturity_value,13)
              else string_concat(v_amount_sign ,amount_temp1) ;
              
              */
              
              out.amount :: if(in.source_indicator=="S" and (decimal(""))in.summary_segment.guaranteed_maturity_value >=0.0 ) string_concat("+",decimal_lpad(in.summary_segment.guaranteed_maturity_value,12)) 
                            else if (in.source_indicator=="S" and (decimal(""))in.summary_segment.guaranteed_maturity_value <0.0 )  decimal_lpad(in.summary_segment.guaranteed_maturity_value,13)
                            else string_concat(v_amount_sign ,amount_temp1) ;


out.aggrement ::  if ( string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I","G","G1","G2","C","F","P" , "R"] ) ""
                  else if(in.source_indicator =="S") 
                         if ( !is_blank( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.hld_holding_name) ) ) string_concat(company_code,in.master_segment.hld_holding_name)  
                         else string_concat(company_code,string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_number))
                  else  string_concat(company_code,string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_number)) ;




out.birth   :: if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) member [ vector  "P" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_1
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) member [ vector  "P" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_2 
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) member [ vector  "P" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_3 
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) member [ vector  "N" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_1
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) member [ vector "N" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_2 
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) member [ vector "N" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_3 
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) == "S" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_1
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) == "S" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_2
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) == "S" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_3
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) not member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) member [ vector "J","L"] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_1
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) not member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) member  [ vector "J","L"]  ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_2
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) not member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3)  member  [ vector "J","L"]  ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_3  ;

               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) member [ vector  "P" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_2
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) member [ vector  "P" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_3

               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) member [ vector  "N" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_2
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) member [ vector  "N" ] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_3
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) == "S" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_1
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) == "S" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_2
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) == "S" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_3
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) not member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) member  [ vector "J","L"] ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_1
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) not member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) member  [ vector "J","L"]) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_2
               else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.account_type) not member [ vector "RRIF" , "LIF" ] and string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) member  [ vector "J","L"]) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_3  ;
               
               


 out.birth_date_2 ::    if(in.source_indicator == "V")
                                if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) == "J" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_1
                                else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) == "J" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_2
                                else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_3) == "J" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_dob_3
                                else " "  
                      
                       else birth_date2 ;

                        if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_1) == "J" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_1
                        else if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.annuitant_type_2) == "J" ) in.master_segment.annuitant_gender_2

                      else gender2;

                                    else '+000000000.00' ;  
                                    


out.ytd_gmwb_withdrawl :: if ( string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I","G","G1","G2","C","F","P" , "R"] ) ""
                          else if ( !is_null(in.master_segment.gmwb_effective_date) and !is_blank(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.gmwb_effective_date)) and
                                          string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.gmwb_effective_date) != "0" and
                                          gmwb_effective_date > lookup("segcons_header_prev_lkp").from_date and
                                          gmwb_effective_date <= lookup("segcons_header_lkp").from_date 
                                        ) "+000000000.00"
                          else if ( ytd_gmwb_withdrawl < 0 ) 
                               string_concat("-",decimal_lpad((decimal(12.2)) math_abs(ytd_gmwb_withdrawl),12))
                          else 
                            string_concat("+",decimal_lpad((decimal(12.2)) ytd_gmwb_withdrawl,12)) ;
                            
                            
out.gmwb_total_fee_factor :: if ( string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I","G","G1","G2","C","F","P" , "R"] ) "" 
                             else if(in.master_segment.gmwb_rider_ind != "N" && (decimal(""))in.master_segment.gmwb_total_fee_factor >=0.0) string_concat("+",decimal_lpad((decimal(""))in.master_segment.gmwb_total_fee_factor,10))
                             else if(in.master_segment.gmwb_rider_ind != "N" && (decimal(""))in.master_segment.gmwb_total_fee_factor < 0.0) decimal_lpad((decimal(""))in.master_segment.gmwb_total_fee_factor,11)
                             else "";


out.next_mv_reset_date :: if ( string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I","G","G1","G2","C","F","P" , "R"] ) "" 
                          else if(in.master_segment.gmwb_rider_ind != "N") in.master_segment.mv_reset_date 
                          else "" ;

out.ride_type_indicator ::  if ( string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I","G","G1","G2","C","F","P" , "R"] ) ""  
                            else in.master_segment.rider_type_ind  ;

out.spousal_income_indicator ::   in.master_segment.spousal_indicator_income ;

out.spouse_date_of_birth :: " " ;



out.life_indicator_1 :: if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.actual_date_of_death_1) == ""  or string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.actual_date_of_death_1) == "0" or !is_valid( (date("YYYYMMDD")) string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.actual_date_of_death_1) ) ) "0"
                        else "1" ;                                        
                        
                        
out.life_indicator_2 ::      if(in.source_indicator == "V")
                                 if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.actual_date_of_death_2) == "" or string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.actual_date_of_death_2) == "0" or !is_valid( (date("YYYYMMDD")) string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.actual_date_of_death_2)) ) "0"
                                 else "1"                         
                             else life_indicator_2;
     
out.actual_date_of_death_1 ::  if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.actual_date_of_death_1) == '0') ' '
                               else in.master_segment.actual_date_of_death_1 ;

out.date_of_notification_of_death_1::    if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.date_of_notification_of_death_1) == ""  or string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.date_of_notification_of_death_1) == "0" or !is_valid( (date("YYYYMMDD")) string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.date_of_notification_of_death_1) )) ''
                                         else string_pad(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.date_of_notification_of_death_1),8) ;                                       

out.actual_date_of_death_2 ::  if(in.source_indicator == "V")
                                    if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.actual_date_of_death_2) == '0') ' '
                                    else in.master_segment.actual_date_of_death_2 
                               else actual_date_of_death_2;

out.date_of_notification_of_death_2:: if(in.source_indicator == "V")
                                            if ( string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.date_of_notification_of_death_2) == '0') ''
                                            else string_pad(string_lrtrim(in.master_segment.date_of_notification_of_death_2),8)   
                                       else date_of_death_notification_2;

out.hnw_agreement_type :: " "  ;
out.agreement_status :: " " ;

out.fund_type :: " " ;

/*
out.fund_type ::  if (  string_like( lookup("fund_lkp",in.fund_lookup_vec).product_series, "%MMP%" ) > 0 ) "MMP"
                  else "R" ;
*/                  

out.fund_management_fee_rate ::  " " ;
out.fund_management_fee_tier :: " " ;
out.advisor_fee_rate :: "";// in.master_segment.advisor_fee_rate ;
out.lib_era :: if (string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I","G","G1","G2","C","F","P", "R"] ) ""
               else if(in.master_segment.gmwb_rider_ind != "N")
                     if(in.master_segment.lib_era =="LIBE1") "1"
                     else if (in.master_segment.lib_era =="LIBE2") "2" 
                     else ""
                     
                else ""    ;
out.income_program_indicator :: if (string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I","G","G1","G2","C","F","P" ,"R"] ) "" 
                                else if(!is_blank(in.master_segment.hld_holding_name)) "Y"      
                                else "N" ;
                                
out.annuity_holding_account_fund_bal_indicator :: " " ;

out.rebate_rate :: " " ;
out.rebate_tier :: "00" ;
out.distribution_chanel :: if (string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I","G","G1","G2","C","F","P" ,"R"] ) "" 
                           else v_distribution_channel;

out.product_name ::  if (string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I","G","G1","G2","C","F","P", "R"] ) "" 
                     else if(in.source_indicator=="S") first_defined(lookup_last("irfi_fund_lkp",in.detail_segment[0].fund_code).product_series,"") 
                     else product_name ;                         //first_defined(lookup("irfi_fund_lkp",first_defined(lookup("Account_investmentInfo_lookup",in.master_segment.account_number).investmentCode,"")).product_series,"");

// Need to check later =====================================================================================================================

out.pac_allocation_percentage :: " "  ;
out.pac_base_amount :: " " ;
out.high_net_worth_invested_indicator :: if (string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I" ] ) 
                                                if (  string_like( lookup("fund_lkp",in.fund_lookup_vec).product_series, "%MMP%" ) > 0 or 
                                                      string_like( lookup("fund_lkp",in.fund_lookup_vec).product_series, "%MME%" ) > 0 
                                                   ) "Y"
                                                else "N"
                                         else if (string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "G","G1","G2","C","F","P", "R"] )  ""
                                         else if(string_prefix(in.master_segment.investment_structure,1) member [vector "A","B"]) "Y"  
                                         else "N" ;


out.gmbr_maturity_benefit_guarantee_amount :: if (string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I","G","G1","G2","C","F","P", "R"] ) "" 
                                              else gmbr_maturity_benefit_guarantee_amount  ;


out.gmbr_maturity_guarantee_date ::  if (string_lrtrim(in.source_indicator) member [ vector "I","G","G1","G2","C","F","P" ,"R"] ) "" 
                                     else if ( string_lrtrim(contract_type) member [ vector "REG-LIF","REG-RRIF","REG-LRIF", "REG-PRIF" ,"REG-RLIF" ] ) 

                                          if ( in.detail_segment[0].policy_maturity_date == 0 ) '21411231'

                                          else string_pad(string_lrtrim(in.detail_segment[0].policy_maturity_date),8,"0")

                                     else

                                          if ( in.detail_segment[0].policy_maturity_date == 0 ) '0'

                                          else string_pad(string_lrtrim(in.detail_segment[0].policy_maturity_date),8,"0") ;



  out.record_count :: in.record_count;

 out.deposit_back_end_charge :: "";//'+00000000.00' ;
 out.deferred_acquisition_amount :: "";//'+00000000.00' ;
 
 
 out.contract_number :: in.detail_segment[0].contract_number ;
